Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.42,0:02:35.34,OPK,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur.5\fad(100,150)}kogetta firumu no youna
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.34,0:02:38.88,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur.5\fad(100,150)}navždy stratená, ako spálený film
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.34,0:02:38.88,OPK,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur.5\fad(100,150)}natsu no kawa ni
