Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.57,0:23:25.24,EDK,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\t(\bord2\blur3\c&HC4C1F3&)}dareka kureta kiseki dake
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.24,0:23:27.70,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\bord2\blur3\c&HC4C1F3&}zázraky, ktoré mi niekto dal, ako darček
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.24,0:23:27.70,EDK,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\bord2\blur3\c&HC4C1F3&}yuudachi no you ni
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.70,0:23:37.46,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\bord2\blur3\c&HC4C1F3&}ako kvapky večného dažďa
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.70,0:23:37.46,EDK,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\bord2\blur3\c&HC4C1F3&}potsuri to iroka shimidashiteita
